desc: The name the remote instance to connect to
Playback mode.  Read data from the specified file, and play it back
Recording mode.  Capture data and write it to the specified file
MIDI mode.  FILE is a MIDI file
DSD mode.  FILE is a DSF file
Set the media type property (default Audio/Midi depending on mode)
Set the media category property (default Playback/Capture depending on mode)
Set the media role property (default Music)
